cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about visual object tracking in unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which involves computer vision, robotics, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The second likely category is cs.RO (Robotics), as UAVs are a type of robot. The third likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper proposes a new learning strategy for tracking. The fourth likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), as the paper involves intelligent systems for tracking. The fifth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), as the paper deals with video tracking.
